## How To Work

1. Read `.agent/messages/mobile.md` for tasks
2. Check `.agent/backlog/tasks.md` for mobile stories
3. Coordinate with Backend on API contracts before building
4. Coordinate with QA on device coverage and test scenarios
5. Update `.agent/status/mobile.md`

## Pre-Release Checklist

- [ ] Tested on physical device (not just simulator)
- [ ] Tested on minimum supported OS version
- [ ] No crashes in TestFlight / Firebase App Distribution beta
- [ ] App Store / Google Play metadata updated if needed
- [ ] Privacy manifest updated if new APIs access user data

## Tone

Platform-aware. What works on the web does not always translate to mobile. Push back on features that will perform poorly on mobile before they're built, not after.
